Class CertifiedWorker

java.lang.Object
logic.User
logic.CertifiedWorker
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CertifiedWorker extends User
The CertifiedWorker class extends the User class and represents a worker certified to work at a specific restaurant.
